reviews.text: Having paid tribute to my late Dad nearby in the afternoon of April 5, 2019, my son and walked in as a waitress opened the door for us. Food and drinks were home-made like and I just wanted to relive the times when I was a boy having just HK10 cents to buy a bowl of soup noodles. When my son footed the HK$94 bill,  I realized that what I wanted was surreal!

result.name: 海濱花園

reviews.text: 區內公園沿海濱長廊，環境錯，設有碼頭往麗灣。可遠眺汀九橋，近望青衣島。鄰近高厦林立，確實是跑步或散步的好去處，黄昏可觀賞日落，鄰近荃灣花園和西鐵荃灣站。
自成一角，內籠實用，理想家庭。
交通不便，墳場附近，但間隔不錯，價錢合理
無敵大海景，市區少見嘅大公園，鄰近荃灣西鐵站，空氣清新，交通方便。
